 />\n<br />\n有時啲人為反而反，反到連自己人都鬥死埋卻不自知，呢啲先係最恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24933e723cca29043816ca84dd98c468f9425e9","tid":2244732,"uid":72994,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"678e8ca7d1b11100edfc47ec7473c3b3dfd1a686","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"138cdb7993e4dbff0673328dd0e7a91291051d47","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00afc916028b00b2d380983a61c62318f3498a82","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"黃店有冇定期捐錢抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解黃店一定要定期捐錢？<br />\n佢又唔係額外收多個客錢<br />\n<br />\n應該話捐錢唔係黃店嘅責任<br />\n而係大家有能力嘅 都應該要出一份力<br />\n同佢係咪黃店無關"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"捐錢唔係責任，咁人地都冇必要一定食黃店啦，你間黃店都0作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"咁嗰啲幫手足比飯錢嗰啲計劃呢？雙十派文宣呢？<br />\n<br />\n人哋好多會請手足做嘢，起碼藍人正常唔會去黃店搵工先<br />\n<br />\n非抗爭日子又有體現人民意志嘅作用，你又有個放心老細唔會督你灰嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n更何況唔係間間都大排長龍，搵大錢，一定要捐先幫襯只會係死循環<br />\n<br />\n而其他商家都係睇錢做人，黃圈有得做佢哋自然會入，但你同人講入場費係一定要捐錢，咪即係落閘趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d4d3cb87ba7fccda680dc4df325a7fba15b76e","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"678e8ca7d1b11100edfc47ec7473c3b3dfd1a686","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"138cdb7993e4dbff0673328dd0e7a91291051d47","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00afc916028b00b2d380983a61c62318f3498a82","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"黃店有冇定期捐錢抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"其