c9dde51","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b24933e723cca29043816ca84dd98c468f9425e9","tid":2244732,"uid":72994,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"678e8ca7d1b11100edfc47ec7473c3b3dfd1a686","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"捐錢唔係責任，咁人地都冇必要一定食黃店啦，你間黃店都0作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"咁嗰啲幫手足比飯錢嗰啲計劃呢？雙十派文宣呢？<br />\n<br />\n人哋好多會請手足做嘢，起碼藍人正常唔會去黃店搵工先<br />\n<br />\n非抗爭日子又有體現人民意志嘅作用，你又有個放心老細唔會督你灰嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n更何況唔係間間都大排長龍，搵大錢，一定要捐先幫襯只會係死循環<br />\n<br />\n而其他商家都係睇錢做人，黃圈有得做佢哋自然會入，但你同人講入場費係一定要捐錢，咪即係落閘趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"啱呀 唔係淨係捐錢先叫付出咗<br />\n做私飯 派文宣 請手足 <br />\n以前仲有遊行嘅時候 又會提供地方休息 免費食物飲品<br />\n到而家大圍捕後 有黃店又會送飯比等候手足嘅家屬<br />\n唔好抹殺大家嘅付出同努力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:58:05.000Z","msg":"姐係乜都冇做啦，講個信字，你比錢佢賺，以後先幫翻你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b710b8078000246ca6d90e1b82b7429481fd1b8","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13d4d3cb87ba7fccda680dc4df325a7fba15b76e","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"678e8ca7d1b11100edfc47ec7473c3b3dfd1a686","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"138cdb7993e4dbff0673328dd0e7a91291051d47","tid":2244732,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解黃店一定要定期捐錢？<br />\n佢又唔係額外收多個客錢<br />\n<br />\n應該話捐錢唔係黃店嘅責任<br />\n而係大家有能力嘅 都應該要出一份力<br />\n同佢係咪黃店無關"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"捐錢唔係責任，咁人地都冇必要一定食黃店啦，你間黃店都0作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:53:10.000Z","msg":"支持黃店係因為佢嘅理念 佢嘅政治立場<br />\n黃店嘅作用並唔係為咗捐錢<br />\n係為咗削弱藍店 中資 紅底商家<br />\n<br />\n捐錢唔係因為黃店呢個身份<br />\n而係作為有良知嘅香港人都可以做嘅事<br />\n唔係幫襯咗黃店 佢賺到嘅錢就一定要拎出嚟捐錢<br />\n佢肯捐當然好<br />\n佢無捐又唔代表可以話佢唔夠黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"姐係零作用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e829000ddf47883ed47aa261062d2b14ef07514","tid":2244732,"uid":287036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:01:06.000Z","msg":"精神"},{"pid":"5df2ac45749b2839f4ddaa5e91bee8f8ea64f8ce","tid":2244732,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c5a3e1a0577733704b2f9589bb1d2f403d546b","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8270a90a658f4f1b43e58c8752809d92c0af5da5","tid":2244732,"uid":231640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d188bed1f4fafa5914165950def555f849cc5451","tid":2244732,"uid":313205,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"955342d3b48395fcb38958275ac13fcf988574e4","tid":2244732,"uid":231640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T22:50:29.000Z","msg":"面果浸係黃 底果浸係藍 點搞?<br />\n零售鋪頭係 黃, 但供應商係藍<br />\n做唔到全黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T22:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實因為成本問題，唔少商家都會選擇大陸入貨，造成零售黃供應藍<br />\n<br />\n我會覺得，都支持咗同路人先啦，唔好因為供應商問題內鬥<br />\n<br />\n換個角度睇，其實如果我哋懲罰得夠入肉，佢哋先有本錢轉供應商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:18:18.000Z","msg":"咁你點知黃鋪選咩供應商"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:02:47.000Z","msg":"因為我地根本離唔開大陸貨源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbf10b655cffac304e4a102349c1abb508a6530","tid":2244732,"uid":216776,"li